# Problem 7 – Count Special Characters

### Code

```python
a = "Hello@123#"

count = 0

for ch in a:
    if not ((ch >= "A" and ch <= "Z") or
            (ch >= "a" and ch <= "z") or
            (ch >= "0" and ch <= "9")):
